tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE website_traffic_data (
    date DATE,
    page_url TEXT,
    user_id INT,
    page_views INT,
    time_spent DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE user_engagement (
    user_id INT,
    email TEXT,
    sign_up_date DATE,
    last_activity_date DATE,
    total_sessions INT
);

CREATE TABLE website_visits (
    visit_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    page_url TEXT,
    device_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE user_activity (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    last_login TIMESTAMP,
    total_visits INT,
    total_engagement_time INTERVAL,
    most_visited_page TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE page_data (
    page_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url TEXT,
    unique_visitors INT,
    bounce_rate FLOAT,
    avg_engagement_time INTERVAL
);

CREATE TABLE website_visits (
  visit_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  visitor_id INT,
  visit_date DATE,
  visit_duration INTERVAL,
  page_visited VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE visitor_demographics (
  user_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR,
  location VARCHAR,
  device_used VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE page_views (
  view_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  visit_id INT,
  page_id INT,
  time_on_page INTERVAL,
  scroll_depth FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE click_events (
  click_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  visit_id INT,
  clicked_element VARCHAR,
  click_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  interaction_type VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE website_users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    registration_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE page_views (
    page_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_name VARCHAR(100),
    user_id INT,
    view_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE user_roles (
    role_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    role_name VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE user_activities (
    activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    activity_name VARCHAR(100),
    user_id INT,
    activity_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE user_sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP
)
